description: Beginning a new three issue series! From Italy comes Andrea Camicâ€™s powerful, beautiful and lush erotic work. In this issue: a romantic tale of a prehistoric couple living in a modern day apartment who show each other how much they can love one another; a man, while resting in a beautiful flower garden, is sexually attacked by the flowers and plants growing around him; a man with an exceptionally large male member is welcomed into the apartment of two astounded young females. Andrea Camic is a remarkably talented cartoonist whose work has appeared in the European magazines Blue and Kiss many times.

In the third and final issue of Andrea Camic's beautiful comic series, the strength of the art is matched only by the dynamic, engaging quality of the storytelling. Based on a story by Italian novelist Celestino Pes, this issue follows the fragile beauty and everpresent cruelty of an all-girls boarding school. Jennifer can only dream of being with her stunning classmate and archenemy, Clara. Or can she make it real? Andrea Camic is an remarkably talented cartoonist whose work has appeared in the European magazines Blue and Kiss many times.

The fourth sexy issue! Artist Andrea Camic's storytelling is too wonderful to say arrivederci quite yet. This issue follows Laura and Katia, two sisters whose innocent walk through the woods turns into a discovery of their grandmother's past, a group of ancient, large-appendaged elves, and their very own destiny. Stunning art from an exceptional creator.
